{"tid":1538530,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"政府唔該你分清楚莊閒先 It is too late to apologize","createTime":"2019-09-04T07:14:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T16:55:49.000Z","uid":217184,"like":36,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"fefd864ab0d36f02c46a850ee503fcdb592c0550","tid":1538530,"uid":217184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:14:07.000Z","msg":"政府唔該你分清楚<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">莊</span></span><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>閒</strong></span></span>先<br />\n<br />\n唔通用咗<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">七八條人命</span></strong></span> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">三隻眼</span></strong></span> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">兩個失蹤不明</span></strong></span> <br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一個嚴重住院</span></span></strong><br />\n只值嚟換撤回？<br />\n  <br />\n你係因為<br />\n怕就嚟<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: brown;\"><strong>9月9號</strong></span></span>美國覆會制裁<br />\n先同我哋講撤回<br />\n怕就嚟<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">10月1號</span></span></strong><br />\n先同我哋講撤回<br />\n怕<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">[black]黑警[/black]</span></strong>到最尾會<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">(被影到)殺咗人</span></span></strong><br />\n先同我哋講撤回<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">All or nothing</span></span></strong><br />\n而家係要求你要實行五大訴求<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">1. 侵侵叫中共還清朝債券&rarr;香港回歸合法性問題<br />\n2. 白衫男以言入罪無辜被黑警打&rarr;香港失去言論自由、警權過大<br />\n3. 太子站黑警濫暴打傷無辜市民 黨鐵拒交CCTV包庇&rarr;警權過大、官商勾結<br />\n4. 太子站黑警拒絕救傷員入內救援傷者&rarr;人道危機<br />\n5. 林鄭錄音流出指特首無權辭職 無能力處理政治問題&rarr;一國兩制已死</span></strong></span></span><br />\n我哋而家係同你玩<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>show hand</strong></span></span><br />\n唔好諗住同我哋<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">講數</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\nIt is too late to apologize <br />\n唔該你唔好再用中共果一套 拉一班 打一班"},{"pid":"286816f3c70fa2c00525b4857384d6fed3f41741","tid":1538530,"uid":217184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:15:34.000Z","msg":"十連推"},{"pid":"d93c7de75a0680318f959be1fe389646e0699a00","tid":1538530,"uid":217184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:17:40.000Z","msg":"我深信撤回只係一個<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">最基本</span></strong>嘅要求<br />\n我哋嘅中心係要成立<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">獨立調查委員會</span></span>同<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">撤回暴動定性</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"5db43ec31f2b503e48de207ecec7bbbf7f1b5992","tid":1538530,"uid":217184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:17:51.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"9a62bd13197ab36d83f386fadfbb3486b7157a2a","tid":1538530,"uid":217184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:18:07.000Z","msg":"2/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"151ba01dfbf5d7a0cee61101a4755dd007099d46","tid":1538530,"uid":124180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:18:57.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幫手share出去 走出同溫層<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4f267ba26088b83aa1750b6c1d5a2e1814bc328","tid":1538530,"uid":62842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:20:03.000Z","msg":"仲有1100+個被捕手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"